ght:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;">【<strong>美食享受</strong>】</span>：<span style="font-size:13px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;">★ 全程享受越南风味餐与特色餐，让您充分感受越南美食；</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;"><span style="font-size:13px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;">【<strong>特别安排</strong>】：</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">★ 赠送滴壶咖啡；</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;">★ 全程豪华旅游大巴接待，赠送每天每人一瓶矿泉水；</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;"><strong><span style="font-size:13px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;">【增值服务】：<span style="font-size:13px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;">★ </span></span></strong><span style="font-size:13px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;"><span style="font-size:13px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;">全程无购物，无自费。</span></span></span><br/></p><p><span style="font-size:13px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;"><span style="font-size:13px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;"><span style="font-size:13px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;"><span style="font-size:13px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;"><span style="font-size:13px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;"></span></span></span></span></span><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>";s:9:"counselor";s:1:"2";s:8:"keywords";s:68:"香港直飞往返【越南】胡志明-头顿•美奈5天纯玩团";s:7:"include";s:2090:"a:9:{s:7:"traffic";a:14:{s:5:"plane";s:1:"1";s:6:"交通";s:189:"往返经济舱机票（团队机票将统一出票，散客机票因实时计价预订后即刻出票）、当地旅游巴士、去程船票，出境港口至香港机场去程交通船票";s:10:"plane_type";s:6:"往返";s:9:"plane_fee";s:99:"经济舱机票（团队机票将统一出票，散客机票因实时计价预订后即刻出票）";s:5:"train";i:0;s:3:"bus";i:0;s: